{"tid":2098061,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"小謝金燕外貌神進化！ 「只改了這裡」90%激似TWICE MOMO","createTime":"2020-07-07T08:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T08:36:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f754226824e8e782f36278e2419046a7e8c461","tid":2098061,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"舒子晨（Nikita）自《大學生了沒》、《超級模王大道2》發跡，外型上亮眼、身材姣好，有小謝金燕之稱。她在6月初換了短髮新造型後頗受好評，近日發出的一張自拍，更被認為激似南韓女團TWICE成員。<br />\n<br />\n舒子晨6日於IG貼出一張近距離自拍照，顏值本來就頗高的她畫上精緻妝容，更加散發仙氣。也有網友發現，她這張自拍的角度和笑容，以及改變化妝方式、凸顯臥蠶的妝容，讓她與南韓女團TWICE成員MOMO相當神似，照片比對過後也真有幾分相似。"},{"pid":"f176bc2491e9b7237fdc288ee588dc62e6969e6c","tid":2098061,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/1NndocR.Et5jFo65GTSvbw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/159aed00-bffc-11ea-b3bf-7cae46800f42\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F1NndocR.Et5jFo65GTSvbw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2F159aed00-bffc-11ea-b3bf-7cae46800f42&h=d2881cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3dJhpiwdKz2Ol1XtjrLt1A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/7f4f4761-bffb-11ea-bdef-a4d403b67171\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3dJhpiwdKz2Ol1XtjrLt1A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2F7f4f4761-bffb-11ea-bdef-a4d403b67171&h=e395f672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FDL5v_GOHnyx5uK3xOnmPQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlna